        <p><strong>Hidden Costs Beyond Settlement:</strong> The direct settlement is only part of the cost. Companies must also pay attorney's fees, expert witnesses, document discovery costs, litigation management, and factor in reputational damage. Many companies report that the total cost of handling an accessibility lawsuit—including legal fees, settlement, and internal costs—exceeds the settlement amount itself.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Serial Litigation Cost:</strong> For companies hit with multiple lawsuits, cumulative costs become staggering. A company sued four or five times can face settlement costs in the millions, plus legal fees and management time.</p>
